sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor C as Client
    participant UV as Uvicorn
    participant R as foods.py router
    participant F as Food model
    participant DB as MySQL

    C->>+UV: GET /foods/1
    UV->>+R: get_food(food_id=1, conn=Depends(get_db))

    R->>+F: Food(conn), food.id=1
    R->>F: food.display()

    F->>+DB: SELECT f.*, r.*\nFROM foods f\nLEFT JOIN recipes r ON f.id=r.food_id\nWHERE f.id=1
    DB-->>-F: rows list

    F->>F: build dict + loop recipeList

    alt rows ว่าง
        F-->>R: None
        R-->>C: 404 {success:false, error}
    else มีข้อมูล
        F-->>-R: {id, nameTh, category, recipeList:[...]}
        R-->>-UV: {success:true, data:{...}}
        UV-->>-C: 200 OK
    end
